          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-white mb-5" style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,52px); letter-spacing:-.03em; line-height:.95;">
            BUILT ON<br><span style="color:#FF6B00;">X1 ULTRACURVE</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-[#888] mb-6" style="font-family:'Archivo Narrow',sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:1.8;">
            Griffix kits are printed exclusively on <strong style="color:#C4AA84;">Substance Inc. X1 UltraCurve</strong> — 6.0mil FLO Technology vinyl engineered alongside factory MX teams for unmatched adhesion to low-surface-energy plastics. Laminated with <strong style="color:#C4AA84;">UltraCurve 1500</strong>, a 15mil premium clear durable overlaminate. Co-developed with Star Racing Yamaha &amp; Monster Energy Kawasaki.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="https://substance.com/products/ultracurve-x1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">LEARN X1 ULTRACURVE</a>
