          <div>
            <div class="font-display text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-wide mb-0.5">Custom Design Service</div>
            <div class="text-[#777] text-sm" style="font-family:'Archivo Narrow',sans-serif;">Fully custom kits matched to your style — from concept to delivery.</div>
